    "question_id" : 79692366,
    "body" : "<p>Yes, by using Android’s <strong>secret code</strong> format (<code>*#*#code#*#*</code>) and a BroadcastReceiver registered for the <code>SECRET_CODE</code> intent, you can open your app’s activity when that code is dialed. Normal dial codes can’t do this.</p>\n",
