    "answer_id" : 79692383,
    "question_id" : 79692366,
    "body" : "<p>You <strong>can use a custom dial code (like <code>*123456#</code>)</strong> to launch your app <strong>via a <code>BroadcastReceiver</code></strong> that listens to outgoing calls or dial actions.</p>\n<h3><strong>But, Google has restricted this heavily since Android 10+</strong> due to privacy and abuse concerns. Still, it’s <strong>possible on older Android versions or rooted devices</strong>.</h3>\n",
